title: CYBERLINK POWER DIRECTOR 3 [ORIGINAL]
description:

                           CyberLink Power Director 3.0  [ORIGINAL]





                              An Overview of Power Director



Introducing the world's fastest and most advanced video editing software program: Power Director. PowerDirector comes complete with the most advanced yet easy-to-use tools for creating professional video productions. Plus, it offers Smart Video Rendering Technology (SVRT) to allow you to complete your movie projects and preserve its quality quicker than any other software program available on the market! PowerDirector even includes a convenient wizard for you to produce movie discs, such as DVD, VCD, SVCD, or MiniDVD without hassles.
